00:00:12.759 --> 00:00:19.642
Hi! Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi

00:00:25.892 --> 00:00:29.437
What are you going to cook for us today?
Chamak Choli (Wheat flour &amp; Milk sweet)

00:00:37.925 --> 00:00:43.825
Ingredients required for Chamak Choli

00:00:43.905 --> 00:00:51.482
Gram Flour, Milk, Sugar, Grated Coconut, Cardamom, Cherries &amp; Ghee

00:01:07.001 --> 00:01:18.621
First boil 250 ml of milk in a pan

00:01:19.905 --> 00:01:40.595
Add 1/2 kg of sugar to the milk &amp; let it dissolve in milk

00:01:42.700 --> 00:01:55.693
Now add grated coconut to the milk &amp; mix it well

00:02:05.611 --> 00:02:25.972
Add 250 gms of gram flour to the milk &amp; mix it well on a low flame for five minutes

00:02:58.067 --> 00:03:06.633
Add cardamom powder to the gram flour paste &amp;
mix it well till it forms into a thick paste

00:03:10.887 --> 00:03:23.621
Now let the gram flour paste to cool down

00:03:39.670 --> 00:03:49.130
Now apply some ghee to the hands &amp;
roll the gram flour mix into a small round balls to form laddus

00:03:50.602 --> 00:04:04.300
Take the laddus into a serving bowl, garnish it with grated coconut, grated carrot &amp; cherry

